chatgpt_solution: We start by computing $\#(50)$. Using the formula $\#N = .5(N) + 1$, we find $\#(50) = .5(50) + 1 = 25 + 1 = 26$. Next, we compute $\#(\#(50))$. Again, we use the formula $\#N = .5(N) + 1$. We plug in $50$ for $N$ and find $\#(\#(50)) = \#(26) = .5(26) + 1 = 13 + 1 = 14$. Finally, we compute $\#(\#(\#50))$. Plugging in $50$ for $N$, we find $\#(\#(\#50)) = \#(14) = .5(14) + 1 = 7 + 1 = \boxed{8}$.
